title: 28 — Searching
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify searching action — search a container or supporter

---

# Search the workbench (supporter in Control Room)
> search workbench
[OK: contains_any "search" "find" "nothing" "empty" "workbench"]

# Search the toolbox (container in Supply Closet, need light)
> take flashlight
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> switch on flashlight
[OK: contains "on"]

> south
[OK: contains "Supply Closet"]

> search toolbox
[OK: contains_any "search" "find" "locked" "closed" "toolbox"]
